  "description": "A panoramic view of a city skyline at dusk or dawn, with a body of water in the foreground. The city is densely packed with buildings, dominated by taller structures towards the center. A long bridge or causeway extends into the water, connecting to the city. The sky is filled with dramatic, layered clouds illuminated with warm hues of orange and pink. The water is calm, reflecting the colors of the sky, creating a serene and picturesque scene. The city appears to be San Francisco, as indicated by the Transamerica Pyramid.",
